casebody.data:
No. 2,076. STATE OF MONTANA ex rel. WYMAN ELLIS et al., Relators, v. J. H. CALDERHEAD, State Auditor, Respondent.

Original.

Writ of mandate. Decided June 18, 1904. Mr. M. 8. Gunn, for Relators. Mr. Jas. Donovan, and Messrs. U. G. & 8. IJ. Mclntire, for Respondent. Per.Curiam.

On consideration, it is now here ordered and adjudged that the motion to quash be and the same is hereby sustained and the proceeding dismissed.
